    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/f19cd3826085ff350c35b8843e9985ab.poster.avif?t=1765010064\" width=610 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/f19cd3826085ff350c35b8843e9985ab.webm?t=1765010064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/f19cd3826085ff350c35b8843e9985ab.mp4?t=1765010064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">探索自上而下的开放世界，探索充满谜题和动感十足的 Boss 战，揭开过去。在实时战略战斗系统中击败敌人。一切都通过传统的逐帧手绘动画变得栩栩如生。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/fff08b0e8396c9d637a01c4211ae84b7.webp?t=1765010064\" width=610 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/245afaad8551d104998d900ae4c1a377.poster.avif?t=1765010064\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/245afaad8551d104998d900ae4c1a377.webm?t=1765010064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/245afaad8551d104998d900ae4c1a377.mp4?t=1765010064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">使用基于图块的移动探索充满谜题的世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">操纵按钮、大炮，甚至牛。将您的环境视为您的个人游乐场，并了解不同的组合如何为您带来成功。驾驶不同的车辆来增强机动性和能力。记住不同物体的行为，以帮助您在面向动作的谜题中快速做出反应。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/d2e1722f1b65301ff9e93ac676bdc0fa.webp?t=1765010064\" width=610 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/663b6e87e64f3dc32f14132c2f220622.poster.avif?t=1765010064\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/663b6e87e64f3dc32f14132c2f220622.webm?t=1765010064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/663b6e87e64f3dc32f14132c2f220622.mp4?t=1765010064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">通过战略性的瓷砖滑动谜题参与战斗。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">周全地协调你的图块放置，以防御敌人的攻击并创造造成伤害的机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">每个角色都拥有独特的三图块组合，依次执行这些操作将导致伤害增强，反击的风险更高。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/481f3ba87447fd9d692e76d63602b49b.webp?t=1765010064\" width=610 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/e7b8d8d2cd287032b3a71d0661edb95d.poster.avif?t=1765010064\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/e7b8d8d2cd287032b3a71d0661edb95d.webm?t=1765010064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/e7b8d8d2cd287032b3a71d0661edb95d.mp4?t=1765010064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在冒险模式中，谜题通常为探索解决方案提供轻松的节奏。但在boss战中，你需要动作快。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">避免老板的攻击，了解他们的模式，然后使用谜题元素来扭转局面。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/b6d9ea9aec14d0b0dcae140cba15b0b8.webp?t=1765010064\" width=610 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/23821122f181a03ecb49eb0c96830238.poster.avif?t=1765010064\" width=610 height=914 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/23821122f181a03ecb49eb0c96830238.webm?t=1765010064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359860/extras/23821122f181a03ecb49eb0c96830238.mp4?t=1765010064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
